      {
        "type": "post",
        "description": "Huge week for Drop Station\u00a0last week\u00a0\ud83d\ude80\ud83d\ude80\n\nWe've outperformed Reddit for Travis and Jason Kelce's (New Heights) podcast fan area! \n\nHuge shout out to Brian Verne, Jake Perlmutter and our partners at Wave Sports + Entertainment who helped New Heights go to #1 on Apple Podcasts and are constantly investing in their growth and pushing the boundaries here.\u00a0\n\u00a0\nNow New\u00a0Heights has a whole new digital experience where...\u00a0\n\u00a0\n1. They have many\u00a0more listeners using\u00a0Drop Station than their reddit group.\n\n2. They are now getting more upvotes than the top reddit posts. \n\nReddit is a well oiled machine and we\u2019re new. We have no push notifications or fancy engagement mechanisms yet either. So I couldn\u2019t be more proud of the team to be driving this engagement so soon.\u00a0Engagement is the cornerstone of growing a podcast audience and is one of the strongest mechanisms to sparks word of mouth.\n\nBest part is we\u2019re just getting started!\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0",
        "url": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7160759744813486080?updateEntityUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_feedUpdate%3A%28V2%2Curn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160759744813486080%29",
